com.ibm.team.scm.client.events

Interface IPatchUpdateEvent


  • public interface IPatchUpdateEvent
    Event that is fired from a workspace connection when the accept queue or current patch changes for one or more components in the workspace.
    Since:
    0.9.0.5 (RTC 4.0.5)
